The variadic.hpp includes the headers in the variadic folder.

Usage

#include <boost/preprocessor/variadic.hpp>

Includes

  • <boost/preprocessor/variadic/elem.hpp> (v)
  • <boost/preprocessor/variadic/size.hpp> (v)
  • <boost/preprocessor/variadic/to_array.hpp> (v)
  • <boost/preprocessor/variadic/to_list.hpp> (v)
  • <boost/preprocessor/variadic/to_seq.hpp> (v)
  • <boost/preprocessor/variadic/to_tuple.hpp> (v)
